{"tid":2357660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2030年「未來人」預言：特朗普連任　人類抵火星","createTime":"2021-01-07T14:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T08:57:49.000Z","uid":271829,"like":9,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f1f8b05b33fc8a1b2d52933a33e8a732a24e40","tid":2357660,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/photo/bknint-20180214110031085-0214_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180214211839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180214110031085-0214_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180214211839&h=b2fba635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n挪亞聲稱來自未來。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n互聯網影片分享平台Youtube一個有10萬人訂閱的頻道，近日邀請了一名自稱來自2030年的男子，在鏡頭前「揭示」即將在12年間發生的事情，包括美國總統特朗普連任成功、2028年抵達火星等。男子接受測謊機試驗，以證明所言屬實，但亦有人質疑箇中真偽。<br />\n<br />\n片段可見，名為挪亞（Noah）的男子隱藏了真正的容貌及聲音，他左手戴上測謊儀，並聲稱自己來自2030年，冒着生命危險透過時光旅行返回現今。他接連道出不少「預言」：如特朗普會成功連任；2030年的總統是名為雷米基（Ilana Remikee）的美國人；；AI發展迅速，能夠控制家居生活；比特幣會比現時更為通用，惟實體貨幣仍未消失。<br />\n<br />\n除了社會發展外，挪亞又指出不少環境「現況」，包括全球暖化令北美溫度上升，但歐洲則變得更冷；人類會在2028年抵達火星，同年發現時光旅行；電動車已和現今汽油及柴油車輛無異；大部分癌症已有痊癒方法。<br />\n<br />\n挪亞更聲稱自己已年屆五旬，但服用藥物後令外表回復如25歲。據測謊儀結果顯示，挪亞所言非虛，但不少網民質疑測試結果被操控，而且測謊儀結果反映受訪者相信自己所言屬實，並非所說的話為客觀事實。亦有人表示，2030年距離現今不遠，挪亞提及的未來美國總統或已出生。"},{"pid":"0a563cdf17f256a3145a7d9329eb6699417d53ea","tid":2357660,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a4d79c06bef94252cba505602d9567cb2ef49f","tid":2357660,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c09a22e999cf7b0c23b157e6f1d3345ac26d386","tid":2357660,"uid":257961,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"玩夠未 <br />\n之前就印度神童"},{"pid":"a617c29c9ffb48a4e96294872898ad1683e5fd4f","tid":2357660,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"2030就有時空旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ae51667572feba8b136e8e09a30441e74ab71a","tid":2357660,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"之前唔知邊度睇度話下一任總統會喺任內瓜老襯"},{"pid":"295b108cfe12b265690c66d324891dae85b60ab3","tid":2357660,"uid":244809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"白卡仔<br />\n我又諗起lunch哥"},{"pid":"98929d31098cf3ecf7b87ed5797ef1eb12d3672b","tid":2357660,"uid":104985,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"男子接受測謊機試驗，以證明所言屬實<br />\n咁我去一轉青山都搵到廿鳩幾個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b7f05a6722a580cd0fc0248787398ff0918182","tid":2357660,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"我預言2030年呢條柒頭唔會再出現"},{"pid":"7e2b5f2ec67c16c16a10db86a2ad850142ce2708","tid":2357660,"uid":211878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"YouTuber搏noise"},{"pid":"c2b80f4764f51740cd5a399753d70fede8dd1b99","tid":2357660,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"你能預測到我而家屌你老母嗎"},{"pid":"7d5956f51344ffcb17b08e2c1236ac23e9e072dd","tid":2357660,"uid":50041,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score